name: Bitcoin Babe Christmas Token
description:
CHRISTMAS SPECIAL TOKEN Features

5.	1/1 ed. will be dropped till the next December i.e. DEC 2022 which will be update via twitter from time to time.

The remaining tokens will be burned on 1st Jan 2022.

Stay tuned.
